A vintage 1960s racing poster style illustration showing two sleek retro-futuristic rockets in a dramatic chase through a star-filled cosmos. The lead rocket is streamlined and gleaming chrome with smooth aerodynamic curves, leaving a brilliant golden trail. Behind it, a bulkier, more antiquated spacecraft with rivets and exhaust pipes struggles to keep pace, trailing gray smoke. The background features a deep navy blue space with stylized speed lines radiating outward, geometric stars, and a distant planet with rings. The color palette emphasizes warm golds, cool teals, and aged cream tones with subtle paper texture throughout, evoking mid-century advertising art and the optimistic space age aesthetic.
